snippet.title: PlayStation - Silent Mobius - Genei no Datenshi (1998) - Intro
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Silent Mobius: Genei no Datenshi is a Role-Playing game, developed by TechnoSoft and published by Bandai Visual, which was released in Japan in 1998.
